met de kak-madam op tafel, veur het petit déjeuner

曠課 ( kuàng kè ) to play truant, to cut classes

香蕉和乒乓球休息室 ( xiāngjiāo hé pīngpāng qiú xiūxí shì ) Banana and table tennis lounge

香	 fragrant, sweet smelling, incense
蕉	 banana; plantain
和	 harmony, peace; peaceful, calm
乒	 used with pong for ping pong
乓	 used with ping for ping pong
球	 ball, sphere, globe; round
休	 rest, stop; retire; do not!
息	 rest, put stop to, end, cease
室	 room, home, house, chamber

банан & пинг-понг гостиная ( banan ping pong gostinaya )

